headline: Keysight Technologies (NYSE:KEYS) Powers AMD's Next-Gen CPU Testing With PCIe 6.0 Integration
summary: Keysight Technologies (NYSE:KEYS) recently collaborated with AMD to advance PCI Express 6.0 technology, marking a significant step in high-speed data transfer and AI application development. Over the past quarter, the company experienced a 3% stock price increase, aligning closely with the market's modest gains. While the market has shown a 10% rise this year and anticipates 15% annual earnings growth, Keysight's performance was supported by its strong Q2 earnings and share buyback...
